BUG-REPORTING
-------------

Please try to reproduce the bug before contacting me.

Things to do when you encountered a bug:

If a core-dump was created:
- start gdb with
   gdb ffma core
- locate the error
   where

If the program exits with a run-time-error:
- start gdb with
   gdb
- run the program
   ffma <used parameter>
- locate the error
   where

send me the following things:
- an extensive description of the situation where the bug happened.
- version of ffma, smapi and fidoconfig
- your config-files
- a short description what system you are using.
